   <abstract xlink:href="http://lib.lsu.edu/services/oralhistory/abstracts/gillis/Morgan_William.pdf">Morgan discusses his association with Gillis Long between 1970 and 1985, Long's
            gubernatorial campaigns, his relationship with John McKeithen, the issue of civil rights
            in Louisiana politics, Long's political fundraising, his work for the Democratic Party,
            his participation on foreign policy issues, his work in Congress, and his
            staff.</abstract>
